body:
***POSSIBLE SPOILERS***

If you don’t know,

there’s a thing going around about how RDJ spoiled A4 in an ad for the Audi e-tron GT (a car). The ad was released December 7, the same day as the trailer.

From what we know from the trailer, Tony Stark is pretty incapacitated with almost no food and no oxygen (what with being stranded in space). But in the possible spoiler video, he said “I get to drive it in Avengers 4.”

So logically, a lot of people think that it means he ends up safe and back on earth where he can drive to his hearts content!

Personally, I think it’s only going to be a flashback.

What do you think it’s going to end up being and why?

Video mentioned is linked here and the quote is at 20 seconds before the end of the 4 minute long video.
